# Design System & Color Tokens

Source: GENERAL_CLAUDE.md § Design System & Color Tokens.

Applies when project has UI or user requests UI work.

## When project HAS a design system

Follow project tokens/theme/CSS variables. Never hardcode colors outside token system.

## When NO design system AND UI work requested

Establish tokens in theme config. Default scaffold (never hardcode hex in components):

| Token | Value | Use |
|-------|-------|-----|
| background | #1a1a2e | Page background |
| surface | #16213e | Cards/panels |
| surface_elevated | #0f3460 | Modals/dropdowns |
| primary | #39FF14 | CTAs, active |
| primary_hover | #2ecc0f | Hover |
| accent | #9B59B6 | Secondary actions |
| text_primary | #FFFFFF | Body text |
| text_secondary | #A0AEC0 | Muted text |
| border | #2D3748 | Borders |
| error | #FC8181 | Errors |
| warning | #F6E05E | Warnings |
| success | #68D391 | Success |

Typography: Inter/sans, JetBrains Mono/mono, 16px base. Spacing: 4px grid. Radius: 8px default, 12px cards.
